description: Welcome to your dream condo in the heart of vibrant South Boston.  This exquisite two-bedroom, two-bath with parking at 362 West Broadway offers a perfect blend of modern luxury and urban convenience.  Spanning 1,284 square feet, this residence boasts an open-concept living area with a balcony.   The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, quartz countertops, custom cabinetry, and a spacious island perfect for entertaining.  The primary suite is a true retreat with a spa-like bathroom featuring a glass-enclosed shower and stunning tile throughout.  Situated in a prime location, 362 West Broadway is just steps away from trendy restaurants, boutique shops, and the best South Boston offers.  Easy access to public transportation and major highways makes commuting a breeze.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional condo in one of Boston's most sought-after neighborhoods.
